# Registration Form Project

## Overview
This project is a simple registration form built with HTML and CSS. It collects user information such as name, email, password, account type, and additional information. The form is designed to be user-friendly and visually appealing.

## Features
- Responsive design that works on various devices
- Input validation for required fields
- Clear labels and placeholders for better user experience
- Ability to upload a profile picture
- Dropdown menu for how users heard about the service
- Terms and conditions acceptance checkbox

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
